H1BEE — Product Requirements Document
Overview
A local-first tool to analyze DOL LCA disclosure data and surface the most practical H-1B sponsoring companies by role, location, and wage. Built to provide deeper, more flexible filtering than existing sites like H1BGrader.
Note for Claude Code
Be concise. Minimize token usage. No verbose comments, no redundant explanations. Keep code tight.
