Data Source
Primary: DOL OFLC LCA Disclosure Data

URL: https://www.dol.gov/agencies/eta/foreign-labor/performance
Format: .xlsx files, one per fiscal year (or partial quarter)
Naming: LCA_Disclosure_Data_FY{YEAR}_Q{QUARTER}.xlsx
Also ingest: LCA_Worksites_FY{YEAR}_Q{QUARTER}.xlsx for multi-site employers

Future (Phase 2): USCIS H-1B Employer Data Hub CSVs for approval/denial rates.
Ingestion

User downloads xlsx files manually from DOL site, drops into data/ folder
ingest.py reads all xlsx files in data/, normalizes columns, deduplicates by CASE_NUMBER, loads into SQLite
Track source file + fiscal year per record
Handle column name variations across fiscal years (DOL changes headers occasionally)
Default filter: only VISA_CLASS = H-1B and CASE_STATUS = Certified

